CREATE TABLE `base_table` (
  `__time` datetime NULL COMMENT "",
  `l5Id` varchar(30) NULL DEFAULT "" COMMENT "",

  `svrIp` varchar(32) NULL DEFAULT "" COMMENT "",
  `mod` varchar(15) NULL DEFAULT "" COMMENT "",
  `cmd` varchar(15) NULL DEFAULT "" COMMENT "",
  `cliBusinessId` varchar(15) NULL DEFAULT "" COMMENT "",
  `svrBusinessId` varchar(15) NULL DEFAULT "" COMMENT "",
  `svrPort` varchar(15) NULL DEFAULT "" COMMENT "",
  `totalSum` float SUM NULL DEFAULT "0" COMMENT "",
  `errSum` float SUM NULL DEFAULT "0" COMMENT "",
  `sucSum` float SUM NULL DEFAULT "0" COMMENT "",
  `ermSum` float SUM NULL DEFAULT "0" COMMENT "",
  `delaySum` float SUM NULL DEFAULT "0" COMMENT "",
  `rejSum` float SUM NULL DEFAULT "0" COMMENT ""
) ENGINE=OLAP 
AGGREGATE KEY(`__time`, `l5Id`, `cliIp`, `svrIp`, `mod`, `cmd`, `cliBusinessId`, `svrBusinessId`, `svrPort`)

DISTRIBUTED BY HASH(`__time`, `svrIp`, `cliIp`, `svrBusinessId`, `cliBusinessId`)

table_meta.db_name.mv_name_1:
CREATE MATERIALIZED VIEW `mv_name_1` (`__time`, `l5Id`, `mod`, `cmd`, `cliBusinessId`, `svrBusinessId`, `totalSum`, `errSum`, `sucSum`, `ermSum`, `delaySum`, `rejSum`)
COMMENT "MATERIALIZED_VIEW"
DISTRIBUTED BY HASH(`svrBusinessId`) BUCKETS 1 
REFRESH ASYNC EVERY(INTERVAL 2 MINUTE)
PROPERTIES (
"replicated_storage" = "true",
"replication_num" = "2",
"datacache.partition_duration" = "10 days",
"datacache.enable" = "true",
"enable_async_write_back" = "false",
"storage_volume" = "builtin_storage_volume"
)
AS SELECT `base_table`.`__time`, `base_table`.`l5Id`, `base_table`.`mod`, `base_table`.`cmd`, `base_table`.`cliBusinessId`, `base_table`.`svrBusinessId`, sum(`base_table`.`totalSum`) AS `totalSum`, sum(`base_table`.`errSum`) AS `errSum`, sum(`base_table`.`sucSum`) AS `sucSum`, sum(`base_table`.`ermSum`) AS `ermSum`, sum(`base_table`.`delaySum`) AS `delaySum`, sum(`base_table`.`rejSum`) AS `rejSum`
FROM `db_name`.`base_table`
GROUP BY `base_table`.`__time`, `base_table`.`l5Id`, `base_table`.`mod`, `base_table`.`cmd`, `base_table`.`cliBusinessId`, `base_table`.`svrBusinessId`;
